page.title: 20THE SURVEY GROUP
page.content: THIS AREA WAS SURVEYED BY CLASS 3 OF WIX COUNTY PRIMARY SCHOOL WITH THEIR HEADMASTER MR.R.BRIDGEWATER.TWO PARENTS, MRS.J.HEATON AND MR.C.THEEMAN ALSO HELPED WITH PROGRAMMING.THE CHILDREN WHO COLLECTED THE SURVEY DATA WERE: *ANDREW WOOD *LISA CUNNINGHAM *MATTHEW GRIFFIN *MICHELLE HEATON *PAUL PAGE *JOANNE CALVERT ELIZABETH SCULLION *LIAN MEACHEN CLARE HOUGHTON *MICHAELA RELF LIZA PHILLIPS *EMMA LONDON RACHAEL FISHER *FIONA MITCHELL CLARE JIGGINS *NICOLE BYE KELLY NICHOLSON *ALASDAIR RITCHIE LEROY GROVES *JOHN WALLS SIMON ANDREWS *RICHARD SWIFT NEIL COY *IAN WOOD ROBERT BOSWELL *THESE CHILDREN START AT THEIR NEW COMPREHENSIVE SCHOOLS IN HARWICH OR THORPE_LE_SOKEN IN SEPTEMBER 1985.
